    <h1>Micro-Influencer</h1>
    <p class="description">A content creator with 10,000–100,000 followers who drives <strong>3–5% engagement rates</strong> and costs a fraction of celebrity partnerships. The go-to format for brands that need authentic reach without megabudgets.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
